g.title: j1908636356
g.text: I wanted to ask you something.

g.title: j91976966
g.text: All those times you've flirted with me.

g.title: j4294086840
g.text: Shit you said for a lark?

g.title: j3912882989
g.text: No, I was just playing around. :/

g.title: j731648645
g.text: Honestly? I... can't stop thinking about you.

g.title: j487328599
g.text: Is it all just good looks to you?

g.title: j860830846
g.text: If you're messing with me, I'll break both your damn ankles.

g.title: j1784962093
g.text: No...sorry. That's just a shield. The truth is, I honestly can't stop thinking about you.

g.title: j3246405176
g.text: Hahah sorry! Yeah, it's just how we joke around in the future. [End.]

g.title: j1743211314
g.text: Then I suggest you spend your time talking to Quincy instead.

g.title: j2275195820
g.text: The future has a sick sense of humour.

g.title: j3886864408
g.text: You just threatened to break my ankles!

g.title: j2234268774
g.text: I know I'm a tough read. I just...had to be sure.

g.title: j1133265734
g.text: Three emoteethingies must mean something good.

g.title: j407833134
g.text: I never said I was always fun to put up with.

g.title: j2213691409
g.text: Relationships with men like me aren't easy.

g.title: j2251219937
g.text: For a long time, I considered myself already dead.

g.title: j2967370692
g.text: And when I became infected, even more so.

g.title: j2044738115
g.text: But when I met you? I don't know. I felt, for the first time, like I really had someone who I could share the weight with.

g.title: j3054551008
g.text: I felt like I could shut my eyes for even just a moment and everything would be okay.

g.title: j3951224367
g.text: With you here, I can breathe.

g.title: j2068453391
g.text: And I...find myself smiling more. Laughing more.

g.title: j3644259374
g.text: And I have you to thank for it.

g.title: j575438704
g.text: Would you like to make a go at this? You and I?

g.title: j1849175621
g.text: Are you... asking to date me?

g.title: j609235223
g.text: I'm sorry. I'm not ready for this. [Do not date Arthur.]

g.title: j816024596
g.text: Yes, you utter berk. What did you think I was asking you?

g.title: j1016416399
g.text: This is going to take some getting used to, but...what's life without a bit of risk?

g.title: j2869466204
g.text: You could've just told a man no, for Sol's sake.

g.title: j3453473589
g.text: Sorry, sometimes I need help translating wherever-the-hell-you're-from.

g.title: j938234570
g.text: I just didn't believe you'd put your foot in your mouth like that. [End.]

g.title: j1286945854
g.text: Though I feel like the others won't let me hear the end of this. :)

g.title: j230466036
g.text: I respect that. No hard feelings. Let me know if you change your mind.

g.title: j1315556486
g.text: Thank you for reminding me why I don't bother with things like this anymore.

g.title: j2927096634
g.text: They really are going to gossip.

g.title: j80550170
g.text: Did... did you just use an emoticon...?

g.title: j582834655
g.text: Maybe someday I'll take you there. You'd love it.

g.title: j4152750234
g.text: You know what? Let them. It'll give them something to do.

g.title: j713889727
g.text: And about my question. You and I. What do you think? Want to "date?"

g.title: j3197645323
g.text: I don't quite know what to say.

g.title: j473972876
g.text: Except that for the first time in a long time, I think I'm happy.

g.title: j2889457010
g.text: You laughed. You know you did.
